## 配置文件结构

配置文件位于 `config/xp_ai_coding_config.yaml`（YAML不可用时自动fallback到JSON）。

```yaml
version: "1.0.0"
project_name: "XPMotors_iOS"
team_name: "小鹏汽车iOS团队"
created_at: "2024-01-01T00:00:00"
updated_at: "2024-01-01T00:00:00"

project_settings: { ... }    # 项目扫描范围
permission_config: { ... }   # RBAC权限配置 → 详见 permissions.md
standards_config: { ... }    # 编码标准规则 → 详见 coding-standards.md
ai_assist_config: { ... }    # AI建议配置
integration_config: { ... }  # Claude Code/Git/CI集成
```

---

## 项目设置配置

```yaml
project_settings:
  language: "mixed"            # swift | objective-c | mixed
  platform: "ios"
  minimum_ios_version: "12.0"
  architecture_patterns: ["MVVM", "MVC", "VIPER"]
  dependency_manager: "cocoapods"

  scan_paths:
    include:
      - "LocalPods/**/*"       # 本地Pod模块
      - "XPApp/**/*"           # 主应用代码
      - "submodule/**/*"       # Git子模块
    exclude:
      - "**/Pods/**"           # 外部依赖（不扫描）
      - "**/build/**"
      - "**/DerivedData/**"
      - "**/.git/**"
      - "**/ThirdParty/**"

  file_patterns:
    source_files: ["**/*.swift", "**/*.h", "**/*.m", "**/*.mm"]
    config_files: ["**/Podfile", "**/*.podspec", "**/*.xcconfig"]
```

